OL,3,CFood inflation jumps to 18-month high
OL,4,Cas chocolate and butter prices rise
OL,6,FFood prices have risen at their
OL,7,Ffastest pace for 18 months amid surges
OL,8,Fin the cost of chocolate, butter and
OL,9,Feggs, latest figures show.
OL,11,FFood inflation lifted to 4.2% this
OL,12,Fmonth from 4% in July, according to
OL,13,Fthe British Retail Consortium (BRC)-
OL,14,FNIQ Shop Price Monitor.
OL,16,FIt marked the highest level since
OL,17,FFebruary 2024.
