OL,3,CFood inflation jumps to 18-month high
OL,4,Cas chocolate and butter prices rise
OL,6,FBosses at the trade body warned that
OL,7,Fthe acceleration in price increases
OL,8,F"adds pressure" to families who are
OL,9,Falready under pressure from the cost
OL,10,Fof living.
OL,12,FFresh food inflation sped to 4.1% for
OL,13,Fthe month on the back of rising dairy
OL,14,Fprices, up from 3.2% in July.
OL,16,FMeanwhile, ambient food inflation
OL,17,Fslowed to 4.2% year-on-year compared
OL,18,Fwith 5.1% in the previous month.
