OL,3,CFood inflation jumps to 18-month high
OL,4,Cas chocolate and butter prices rise
OL,6,FThe new figures also showed that
OL,7,Foverall shop price inflation increased
OL,8,Fto 0.9% in August, despite price
OL,9,Fdeflation of 0.8% for non-food
OL,10,Fproducts.
OL,12,FThe uptick in food prices comes after
OL,13,Fthe Bank of England said earlier this
OL,14,Fmonth that the increase in national
OL,15,Finsurance contributions in April had
OL,16,Fcontributed to accelerating food
OL,17,Fprices.
