OL,3,CFood inflation jumps to 18-month high
OL,4,Cas chocolate and butter prices rise
OL,6,FHelen Dickinson, chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe BRC, said: "Shop price inflation
OL,8,Fhit its highest rate since March last
OL,9,Fyear, fuelled by food price rises.
OL,11,F"This adds pressure to families
OL,12,Falready grappling with the cost of
OL,13,Fliving.
OL,15,F"Retailers continue doing everything
OL,16,Fthey can to limit price rises for
OL,17,Fhouseholds, but as the Bank of England
OL,18,Facknowledged, the #7 billion in new
OL,19,Fcosts flowing through from last year's
OL,20,Fbudget has created an uphill battle
OL,21,Ffor retailers."
