OL,3,CFood inflation jumps to 18-month high
OL,4,Cas chocolate and butter prices rise
OL,6,FMore than 60 retail bosses, including
OL,7,Fchiefs at Tesco, Sainsbury's and
OL,8,FBoots, warned Chancellor Rachel Reeves
OL,9,Flast week that raising taxes further
OL,10,Fin the autumn budget could contradict
OL,11,Fher plans to improve UK living
OL,12,Fstandards.
OL,14,FIn the letter, co-ordinated by the
OL,15,FBRC, the bosses said they were
OL,16,Fexpecting the rate of food and drink
OL,17,Finflation to reach 6% later this year.
